### Get published events sorted by startDate
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=status eq 'Published'&$orderby=startDate

### Get events filtered by type Workshop
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=type eq 'Workshop'

### Get all registrations for a specific event
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/event/Registrations?$filter=event_ID eq 'E001'

### Create a new registration
POST http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/event/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "R001",
  "event_ID": "E001",
  "attendeeName": "Rahul Kumar",
  "email": "rahul@example.com"
}

### Get speakers sorted by rating descending
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/event/Speakers?$orderby=rating desc

### Get events with available seats
GET http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=registeredCount lt maxAttendees

### Change event status from Draft to Published
PATCH http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/event/Events('E001')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Published"
}

### Add feedback for an event
POST http://port4004-workspaces-ws-76zvt.ap21.trial.applicationstudio.cloud.sap/odata/v4/event/Feedbacks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID": "F001",
  "event_ID": "E001",
  "rating": 5,
  "comments": "Excellent workshop!"
}